    .contacts (itemprop="address" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/PostalAddress")
      | г.
      span< itemprop="addressLocality" Москва
      | ,
      strong< itemprop="streetAddress" Варшавское шоссе, д. 33, стр. 13

      ya-map.map-contacts (
        ya-controls="smallMapDefaultSet"
        ya-zoom="13"
        ya-center="[37.623278, 55.691699]"
      )
        ya-geo-object (
          ya-source="{ geometry: { type: 'Point', coordinates: [ 37.623278, 55.691699] }}"
          ya-options="{ iconLayout: 'default#image', iconImageHref: '#{asset_url('site/marker.png')}', iconImageSize: [45, 49], iconImageOffset: [-15, -35] }"
        )

